Alfred Burke https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alfred_Burke 0 Alfred Burke (28 February 1918 – 16 February 2011) was an English actor, best known for his portrayal of Frank Marker in the drama series Public Eye, which ran on television for ten years.
